    "Although a frank Hegelian account of the period, his hermeneutical method also showed an influence of <a href=\"/winckelmannj\">Johann Joachim Winckelmann</a> and the philosophers Friedrich Schelling (1775-1854), Karl Solger (1780-1819).": [],
